snippet.title: Amber heard and elon musk fuel reunion rumours
snippet.description:
Amber heard and elon musk fuel reunion rumours 
The Danish Girl star met up with Musk in Los Angeles on Thursday 21Dec17, and in pictures obtained by TMZ, the former couple is seen embracing outside the restaurant and appearing to lock lips before getting into separate cars. It was the second time the pair had been photographed together in public since parting ways in August 17 – the exes also stepped out for breakfast last month Nov17, a day after Musk opened up about painful split in an interview with Rolling Stone magazine. “I just broke u...
